translation: When the golden swallow's tears overflow...{LF}the world's mirror will shatter into a{LF}rainbow of color.{#Name="Three"}
source: When the golden swallow's tears overflow...{LF}the world's mirror will shatter into a{LF}rainbow of color.{#Name="Three"}

translation: Ugh. Like I need this nonsense right now.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Ugh. Like I need this nonsense right now.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Gray runs through the wood.{LF}Darkness passes. A curtain parts...{#Name="Three"}
source: Gray runs through the wood.{LF}Darkness passes. A curtain parts...{#Name="Three"}

translation: What's that mean, huh? What's it mean?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: What's that mean, huh? What's it mean?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Don't worry about it. I doubt it means anything.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Don't worry about it. I doubt it means anything.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Red runs through the sky.{LF}The soul's stairway spans the evening star...{#Name="Three"}
source: Red runs through the sky.{LF}The soul's stairway spans the evening star...{#Name="Three"}

translation: ...The soul's what now?{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...The soul's what now?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Blue runs through the sands.{LF}A one-armed rabbit chases a future lizard.{#Name="Three"}
source: Blue runs through the sands.{LF}A one-armed rabbit chases a future lizard.{#Name="Three"}

translation: ......{#Name="Zero"}
source: ......{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Have you any reaction to these poems, my lady?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Have you any reaction to these poems, my lady?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: I'm tired of this shit. How's that?{#Name="Zero"}
source: I'm tired of this shit. How's that?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: ...What is it? You finally done?{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...What is it? You finally done?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: The nimble dog arises from the underworld,{LF}sounding a drumbeat from the grass...{#Name="Three"}
source: The nimble dog arises from the underworld,{LF}sounding a drumbeat from the grass...{#Name="Three"}

translation: I knew that was coming.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I knew that was coming.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: A maiden's footpads trample grass,{LF}giving way to thorns.{#Name="Three"}
source: A maiden's footpads trample grass,{LF}giving way to thorns.{#Name="Three"}

translation: Dance. Dance! The fiery embers{LF}dance up to the promised land.{#Name="Three"}
source: Dance. Dance! The fiery embers{LF}dance up to the promised land.{#Name="Three"}

translation: The visions in your mind are but phantoms.{LF}They soar and return to the grave.{#Name="Three"}
source: The visions in your mind are but phantoms.{LF}They soar and return to the grave.{#Name="Three"}

translation: The swallow's breath becomes a shackle,{LF}burying twin strawberries in the world's depths.{#Name="Three"}
source: The swallow's breath becomes a shackle,{LF}burying twin strawberries in the world's depths.{#Name="Three"}

translation: Three...{#Name="Zero"}
source: Three...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero... I screwed up...{#Name="Three"}
source: Zero... I screwed up...{#Name="Three"}

translation: I invited One to the forest...so I could kill her, but...{#Name="Three"}
source: I invited One to the forest...so I could kill her, but...{#Name="Three"}

translation: She's... Be careful...{#Name="Three"}
source: She's... Be careful...{#Name="Three"}

translation: Is she dead? She's totally dead!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Is she dead? She's totally dead!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: has led to a wide range of observed anomalies.{#Name="235"}

translation: are now acting independently of one another.{#Name="469"}

translation: Statues of Lady Three, it would seem.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Statues of Lady Three, it would seem.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: She never did make any goddamn sense.{#Name="Zero"}
source: She never did make any goddamn sense.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: The exit hasn't opened up.{#Name="Zero"}
source: The exit hasn't opened up.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Is there something hidden within{LF}Lady Three's statues, perhaps?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Is there something hidden within{LF}Lady Three's statues, perhaps?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Quit your yapping, you stupid mutts!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Quit your yapping, you stupid mutts!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Pieces of shit need to hurry up and die!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Pieces of shit need to hurry up and die!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Pieces of shit? So predictable.{LF}Maybe try pus-encrusted boils next time?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Pieces of shit? So predictable.{LF}Maybe try pus-encrusted boils next time?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Can I swap you guys out for a new party?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Can I swap you guys out for a new party?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Is that a...a cerberus?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Is that a...a cerberus?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: A particularly ugly and horrid{LF}example of the species.{#Name="Octa"}
source: A particularly ugly and horrid{LF}example of the species.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: So long as it dies like all the rest, I'm good.{#Name="Zero"}
source: So long as it dies like all the rest, I'm good.{#Name="Zero"}
